address1: Yueyang Economic and Technological Development Zone
longBusinessSummary: Huayu Expressway Group Limited, an investment holding company, invests in, builds, operates, and manages infrastructure projects in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Qing Ping Expressway and Liquor and Spirits segments. The company constructs, operates, and manages the Qing Ping Expressway. It also distributes liquor and spirits under the Huamaojiu and Xijiushaofang brand names. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Yueyang, the People's Republic of China. Huayu Expressway Group Limited is a subsidiary of Velocity International Limited.
